{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2016/09/22/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h1>Hardware</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.fischl.de/usbtin/\">USBtin</a> - USBtin is a simple USB to CAN interface. It can monitor CAN busses and transmit CAN messages. USBtin implements the USB CDC class and creates a virtual comport on the host computer.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T19:24:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h1>Hardware</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://canb.us/\">CANBus Triple</a> - General purpose Controller Area Network swiss army knife and development platform.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T19:21:01.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h1>Hardware</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/jcdemay/canspy\">CANSPY</a> - A platform giving security auditors to audit CAN devices. It can be used to block, forward or modify CAN frames on the fly autonomously as well as interactively.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T19:13:46.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Applications</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://rbei-etas.github.io/busmaster/\">BUSMASTER</a> -An Open Source tool to simulate, analyze and test data bus systems such as CAN, LIN, FlexRay.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T19:07:52.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Applications</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/eik00d/CANToolz\">CANToolz</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/eik00d/CANToolz\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-famil