ic Docker Container Images for Erlang/OTP.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T14:26:22.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers","categoryHTML":"<h2>Retro</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>PongSaver</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PongSaver is an macOS screensaver/clock which keeps time by using the score of a game of Pong. The left side wins once an hour, and the right side wins once a minute.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://mikeash.com/software/pongsaver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/pongSaver.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T14:24:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers","categoryHTML":"<h2>Developer</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Developer Excuses</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A macOS Screensaver which shows quotes from <a href=\"http://developerexcuses.com\">http://developerexcuses.com</a> (unofficial).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kimar/DeveloperExcuses\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/developerExcuses.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T14:24:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"thangchung/awesome-dotnet-core","categoryHTML":"<h2>Frameworks, Libraries and Tools</h2><h3>API</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Azure/autorest\">autorest</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Azure/autorest\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3982,\"repo\":\"Azure/autorest\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Swagger (OpenAPI) Specification code generator featuring C# and Razor templates. Supports C#, Java, Node.js, TypeScript, Python and Ruby. <code>4.5.x or above</code></li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T07:40:28.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"thangchung/awesome-dotnet-core","categoryHTML":"<h2>Frameworks, Libraries and Tools</h2><h3>ORM</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/schotime/NPoco\">NPoco</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/schotime/NPoco\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">807</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":807,\"repo\":\"schotime/NPoco\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Simple microORM that maps the results of a query onto a POCO object. Project based on Schotime's branch of PetaPoco.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T07:29:02.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/gesquive/git-user\">git-user</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/gesquive/git-user\">git-user</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/gesquive/git-user\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">37</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":37,\"repo\":\"gesquive/git-user\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></h2>\n<pre><code># add a work profile for Henry\n$ git user add work \"Dr. Henry Jekyll\" henry@jekyll.com\nAdded profile 'work'\n\n# add a personal profile for Edward\n$ git user add home \"Edward Hyde\" hyde@night.com\nAdded profile 'home'\n\n# list out our saved profiles\n$ git user list\nGlobal Profile:\n  User: Henry &#x3C;hjekyll@gmail.com>\n\nSaved Profiles:\n  home: Edward Hyde &#x3C;hyde@night.com>\n  work: Dr. Henry Jekyll &#x3C;henry@jekyll.com>\n\n# set the current git repository user to the home profile\n$ git user set home\nThe user for the 'project' repository has been set too 'Edward Hyde &#x3C;hyde@night.com>'\n\n# list profiles again, notice how the current repository profile is now set\n$ git user\nProject Profile:\n  Path: /path/to/git/project\n  User: Edward Hyde &#x3C;hyde@night.com>\n\nSaved Profiles:\n  home: Edward Hyde &#x3C;hyde@night.com>\n  work: Dr. Henry Jekyll &#x3C;henry@jekyll.com>\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T01:02:31.000Z"}]}},"pageContext":{"type":"day","from":1474502400000,"to":1474588799999,"previousId":"2016-09-23","nextId":"2016-09-21","nextName":"Sep 21st, 2016","previousName":"Sep 23rd, 2016"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","2828988102"]}